# Kooslab Landing Page SvelteKit Project Rules

## Package Management

- Use pnpm instead of npm for all package management operations.

## UI Components

- Use Bits UI components whenever possible for consistent UI design.

## Svelte Coding Standards

- Use the Svelte 5 syntax with `onclick` instead of `on:click` directives.
- Follow SvelteKit conventions for routing and API endpoints.

## Email Services

- The project uses Resend email service with a verified domain (mail.kooslab.net).
